  "texts": [
    "The non-repeated-measure design included 107 radiologists in a non-repeated-measure setup (Supplementary Fig. 1).",
    "Each radiologist read 60 patient cases across four subsequences that each contained 15 cases.",
    "Each subsequence corresponded to one of four treatment conditions: with AI assistance and clinical histories, with AI assistance and without clinical history, without AI assistance and with clinical histories and without AI assistance and clinical histories.",
    "The four subsequences and associated treatment conditions were organized in a random order.",
    "The 60 patient cases were randomly selected and randomly assigned to one of the treatment conditions."
  ],
